This project is an Spring social extension for weibo website.

If you are using this project, you should probably consider to read the term of use of Weibo:
http://open.weibo.com/wiki/%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To get the code and build from source, do the following (I assume Maven is already installed):

git clone --recursive git://github.com/vergnes/spring-social-weibo.git
cd spring-social-weibo
mvn clean install

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To import project in Eclipse using M2clipse plugin
File -> Import -> Existing Maven project
Follow wizard's instructions
